# SSS Application
API Mockup for SSS application

# Group Categories
API for **Category**

## Categories Collection [/categories]
### List all Categories [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            X-Application: ZGVtb2RlbW9kZW1v
            
    + Body
    
            {
            "code": 0,
            "data": [
                    {
                      "id": 1, "name": "Nokia"
                    }, 
                    {
                      "id": 2, "name": "Apple"
                    }
                ]
            }

## Category [/category/{id}]
Get detail of a category

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Id of a category

### Retrieve detail of a Category [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-Application: ZGVtb2RlbW9kZW1v

    + Body
    
            {
                "code": 0,
                "data": { 
                    "id": 1, 
                    "name": "Nokia"
                }
            }
            
