# Group Users
API for **User**

## User [/user/{uid}/{token}]
Get detail of a user

+ Parameters
    + token (required, string, `abcdefghj`) ... Facebook Token
    + uid (required, string, `hnq90`) ... Facebook User Id

### Retrieve detail of a User [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-Application: ZGVtb2RlbW9kZW1v

    + Body
    
            {
                "code": 0,
                "data": {
                    "id": 9, 
                    "name": "HuyNQ",
                    "type": 1,
                    "token": "abcdefghj",
                    "uid": "hnq90"
                }
            }
